The Palm Coast Farmers Market takes place every Sunday from noon-4 pm in the Courtyard of European Village. The Restaurants and Bars are also open for a sit down drink or meal for your enjoyment as well. The Farmers Market features dozens of vendors displaying their original work, selling quality food items, giftware and more. Extra parking available under the bridge.
